{"type": "article", "id": 32133, "title": "这套有脚的托盘，想让你的餐桌变得有层次｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-12T23:08:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28984, "name": "Something"}, {"id": 32691, "name": "SUWU Design Studio"}, {"id": 7058, "name": "造作"}, {"id": 32692, "name": "Luca Nichelo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 182, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160912234626BUt6LGXfCyKD3ok4.jpeg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Stage &amp; Momento by Something</h3><p>由 Daniel Debiasi 和 Federico Sandri 成立的 <a href=\"http://www.somethingdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Something</a> 设计工作室最近为 Normann Copenhagen 打造了两款简洁风格的灯具，分别是落地灯 Stage 和台灯 Momento。Stage 的锥形灯罩顶端有一个可以用来调整灯光方向的把手，整体造型容易让人联想到摄影棚里的专业器材。Momento 则是以钓竿作为灵感设计的，在保持底座不动的情况下，它的灯柱能够在管状的支撑架上滑动，就像是在调整钓鱼线的长度一样。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234811MJh3dqpsxSNm0cT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.282396\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609122348112u5gbnWM96tNj4BQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234811jCRe3HWa6zDciJQd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234812OFdbwS9cPE8QvReH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.319071\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234811IiDCLacBUsrF2TH4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234811i0aApHsYltuOGfJE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LW-01 by SUWU Design Studio</h3><p>在探索如何更好地利用矿泉水瓶的时候，<a href=\"http://www.suwudesign.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">素物创新工作室</a>的设计师们想出了一个奇妙的点子，由此诞生了这个名为 <a href=\"https://competition.adesignaward.com/design.php?ID=47267\" rel=\"nofollow\">LW-01</a> 概念设计。它是一个直径 2.2 厘米、长 5 厘米的瓶盖附件，适用于市面上大部分瓶盖，专门用来放置药物，可以免去额外携带药盒的麻烦。在灾后救援或是安抚幸存者的场合，救援人员能够借此向人们同时提供饮用水和应急药物，增加了效率。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609122348387K0A6NWlqSdvDsPk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234837eO2YZMv0WzjS15uC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234838Kzw3TLZioblPVvBD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234838KaW9QflbHMYepnXU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>DUOECHO by DUOECHO Team</h3><p>当你第一眼看到这款由台湾设计团队带来的 DUOECHO 蓝牙音响时，或许会觉得它和市面上那些像随身杯一样的便携式蓝牙音响并没有什么差别。实际上，它是由两个分离式的音响组合而成的，只有动手“拆开”才能让它大显身手。设计师们以竹子简约的造型为启发，通过精密计算打造出的曲线以及磁性吸附式设计让两个音响能够轻松地合二为一，轻薄强韧的铝合金外壳更是极具质感。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1567985175/duoecho-hi-fi-bluetooth-stereo-speaker-with-magnet\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 159 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234928kj9pQaDRtXdGHyJs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234925H3y1Cs25PvxJo6Wq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234925LKPOp8sGxejf49DJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234926hFXxG19BTwbjHtDE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234931ISd7VCAwrJMnOhFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LetB by Olek Krupa</h3><p>来自华沙的 Olek Krupa 是一名在伦敦求学的机械工程系学生，这款让人眼前一亮的画框型时钟 LetB 就是他亲手打造的。Krupa 抛弃了传统的钟面设计，通过亮起的单词来表示时间。尽管 LetB 每五分钟才更新一次时间，Krupa 这个独特的创意还是开拓了时钟设计的可能性，同时也能给予人们一些启发，换一种角度审视身边寻常的物品。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/220465991/letb-display-time-by-text\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 50 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234747Y3CMFPalDUfEJIxh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234747v4MQY6h17CgfXGU8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609122347470KcplOIZSULnQtgV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609122347475LeENlJ3AjFmcYyf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234747qthDvU0eSKO5PFXd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234747VTQ01cra7Oqx4LNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cayman Trays by Luca Nichelo</h3><p>意大利设计师 <a href=\"http://nichettostudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Luca Nichelo</a> 最近为<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">造作</a>设计了一套名为 Cayman 的嵌套式置物托盘，在造型上参考了意大利传统的农作工具挤奶凳（milking stool）。它的主体与腿部采用螺纹连接，每条腿底都附有防滑的毛毡垫，在保护接触面的同时也避免托盘在挪动时产生噪音。大中小三种尺寸嵌套在一起放在餐桌上可以让摆盘方式变得更加立体有趣，除此之外还能用作小桌放上蜡烛或是其他装饰品，适用于各类场合。这是它的<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300121\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 366 元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234655426GX9Jj1kRZABwY.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609122346552Da8rYESJnVGF7tz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234656R72VyI3Q8STAtEwk.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234656WZn9xjPLMwJEYUF6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.408854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609122346571oNzVZxFSLsGO6Td.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.408854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234658mXFH8oIU3VO94gay.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tallinn Doors Chocolate by Kristi Tamming</h3><p>如果你打算去爱沙尼亚旅游，这个名为 Tallinn Doors 的巧克力系列不光能满足你的味蕾，还能带你去看当地具有特色的建筑。由 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/kristitamming\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kristi Tamming</a> 设计的三款巧克力包装分别对应了一扇你能在塔林古城找到的的门，包装背面的上半部分印有关于这座建筑的历史故事，只要扫描底部的二维码你就能定位到它所在的位置，借助导航看一看实景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234723SqRDbXdEMU3TFBJ5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234724xku2KB39HmTIvejO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234724b5Mgr26IOpKovkDj.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234722ecGY0tzwiK7BROUS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160912234723h9DwZ2u37KN8dXrH.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609122347236nMWIl4JH3EgRpQj.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}